Module Mal4J
Package com.kttdevelopment.mal4j

Class MyAnimeList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kttdevelopment.mal4j.MyAnimeList
  • public abstract class MyAnimeList
extends Object
    The MyAnimeList API interface, used to execute requests with the API from Java.

    The MyAnimeList class can be created by authenticating with either:
    • An oauth token using withOAuthToken(String)
    • An authorization code and client id using withAuthorization(MyAnimeListAuthenticator).
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    2.4.0
    Author:
    Katsute
